21#include "mpc-impl.h"
22
23void
24mpc_swap (mpc_ptr a, mpc_ptr b)
25{
26 /* assumes real and imaginary parts do not overlap */
27 mpfr_swap (mpc_realref(a), mpc_realref(b));
28 mpfr_swap (mpc_imagref(a), mpc_imagref(b));
29}
